{"tid":2277176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★劏房人均面積僅40.7平方呎　較3年前大幅下降近10平方呎  比囚倉更細","createTime":"2020-11-08T09:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T09:25:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"999b77f334acc429d8df4a9d4e8b1d87b6d5ac30","tid":2277176,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:21:09.000Z","msg":"香港土地寸金尺土，劏房、天台屋等應運而生，成為本港低下層的哀歌。葵涌劏房居民大聯盟今日(8日)發表不適切居所住戶的住屋狀況調查報告，發現在這些居所的人均居住面積僅40.7平方呎，較3年前的大幅下降近10平方呎，而過半受訪者更被濫收水電費，亦沒有獨立廚房，存在安全隱憂。大聯盟促請政府落實租務管制、訂立住屋標準，並為改善居住環境制訂具體目標和時間表。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201108/bkn-20201108140156765-1108_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201108%2Fbkn-20201108140156765-1108_00822_001.html&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7w4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=f565d2d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201108/bkn-20201108140156765-1108_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d836ef1c9a4ba40bc94bc4855d7fd8d3cbdb9a3f","tid":2277176,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4oHagK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4oHagK.jpg&h=eb3bb700&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48111a46802a5ec95ca57d32f4c08a8c8d6ec7d7","tid":2277176,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"劏房好 寒窗苦讀 可以鍛煉意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHard time makes strong men"},{"pid":"856646bbe2a0773ec4d221e1d332abefcc755fca","tid":2277176,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"Le d大聯盟又想搭雞棚sell great bay area or 大嶼人工島"}]}